3. The following public service bodies are prescribed, for the purposes of 
section 107(6)(a), as public service bodies from which representatives may be 
appointed to the Steering Group: 

(a) 

the Child and Family Agency; 

(b) 

the Commissioners of Public Works in Ireland; 

(c) An Garda Síochána; 

(d) 

the Health Service Executive; 

(e) An Ghníomhaireacht um Fhoréigean Baile, Gnéasach agus 

Inscnebhunaithe.
